OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy cloud first thing
OL,6,Fwith some mist and fog patches, but
OL,7,Flifting to leave plenty of sunshine
OL,8,Fthrough the day. Feeling warm for many
OL,9,Fas winds remain light throughout.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud starts to move in from
OL,12,Fthe west overnight which can produce
OL,13,Fsome spots of rain at times. Another
OL,14,Fmild night to come, albeit slightly
OL,15,Fbreezier.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,18,Fweekend but lifting and breaking
OL,19,Fthrough the morning to leave plenty of
OL,20,Fbright and sunny spells. Staying
OL,21,Fbreezy but feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
