OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure continues to build through
OL,7,Fthe weekend, becoming increasingly
OL,8,Fsettled. Temperatures will climb day
OL,9,Fby day, feeling very warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
